summary: Large, custom playerhouse mod containing a lot of custom textures ( high ress )
descriptionHtml:
[COLOR=#b8cce4][B]Svindall Estate[/B][/COLOR] is a large playerhouse mod for Skyrim. Unfortunately, because of the time I have available working on this mod, which isnt a lot at the moment, I decided to upload the interior at least. Anyone who feels like going into the CK and continue this work is free to do so, just give me credits for the original :D

I\'m probably going to open my box of 3dmodeling skills in Blender or 3DSMax and continue this project all customized, including the architecture and meshes. This version can be seen as a modder\'s resource

To get into the Estate, type \"[B][U][COLOR=#b8cce4]coc 00SvindallEstateInt[/COLOR][/U][/B]\" in the ingame console.

Some of you might not think it\'s entirely lore-friendly because of the new textures. I however think it is ;)

Enjoy!
